00:33:16.470 --> 00:33:18.220
catching a falling knife, right?

00:33:18.220 --> 00:33:20.210
Where the market is falling.

00:33:20.210 --> 00:33:21.680
It's getting
cheaper and cheaper.

00:33:21.680 --> 00:33:24.519
But then it proceeds to
get cheaper still, right?

00:33:24.519 --> 00:33:26.560
Once this got to 10, you
would say, that's cheap.

00:33:26.560 --> 00:33:27.130
