Market cap weighting
means you're

00:39:20.670 --> 00:39:23.056
investing based on
the broad portfolio.

00:39:23.056 --> 00:39:24.930
You invest the most in
the biggest companies.

00:39:24.930 --> 00:39:29.300
Right now, that's what Exxon,
Apple-- certainly up there.

